"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-sport-olympics-alex-yee-olympics-gold-paris-team-gb\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Alex Yee was delighted after winning gold at the Paris Olympics on Wednesday  GETTY  ByJack Otway,  Published: 31/07/2024  The 26-year-old has etched his name into the history books  Team GB star Alex Yee has opened up after his sensational exploits in the men's triathlon on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}, {\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 97, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\", \"score\": 0.9979114343125464, \"rank\": 0.002092883837929768, \"text\": \"Otway\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.2358290699044558e-11, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old managed to beat New Zealand's Hayden Wilde and France's L\\u00e9o Bergere to become the latest Briton to secure a place at the top of the podium.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8519048435555777, \"rank\": 0.12941532318046242, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 349, \"end\": 355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5141005711207867, \"rank\": 0.6327745724874034, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There had been doubts over whether the event would go ahead amid concerns over the pollution levels of the River Seine.Organisers had previously said there was only a 60 per cent chance of the waters being fit for humans to compete in but, after a check at 03:20 on Wednesday, results from the latest water analyses deemed conditions compliant.Alex Yee was delighted after winning gold at the Paris Olympics on Wednesday|GETTYYee initially struggled, with the Briton down in 23rd during the cycling.However, he upped the ante and turned things around to battle his way into the lead during the 10km run.It looked as though Wilde would reign supreme when he closed the gap.But Yee was able to turn things around and overtake his fellow competitor, with the Team GB star eventually winning by six seconds.JUST IN:Emma Raducanu appears to take swipe at Judy Murray with 'astonishing' comment after new mixed doubles inviteAfter the event, the 26-year-old said he had 'so much respect' for Wilde - showing he's a class act in the process.\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9971935377546614, \"rank\": 0.0028142395469074855, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 1199, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.2358290699044558e-11, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}, {\"begin\": 1293, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Judy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have so much respect for Hayden and how much he made me dig there,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Hayden\", \"score\": 0.9999999997739906, \"rank\": 2.258999896248199e-10, \"text\": \"Hayden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Hayden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Hayden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was an amazing athlete and for me, almost two laps in I thought that silver was on the cards but I owed it to myself to give myself one last chance.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With about 2km to go I thought I'd give it everything I had and I am just so proud that I was able to do that for my family, for everyone that's worked hard, for my girlfriend Liv - there is so many more people than just me who have worked towards this.READ MORE:'Disqualify them' - Olympic officials told to boot Rafael Nadal and Carlos Alcaraz out of doubles draw\\\"This was our dream and I am the lucky one who gets to do it, so thank you to them.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 2157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I gave it everything I had and I was going through a really bad patch.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Many people have told me that you are gonna go through a bad patch during a race no matter how perfect or bad it is, so I think for me I just rode that wave and said one more try and let us see if we can do it.\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"LATEST SPORTS NEWS:Mike Tyson receives 'devastating' warning as controversy continues to surround Jake Paul fightOlympics athletes 'think there is a huge issue brewing in Paris' after Adam Peaty's positive Covid testAdam Peaty update provided by Team GB team-mate as Olympics dream hangs in the balanceAlex Yee sent a nice message to Hayden Wilde after winning gold at the Paris Olympics|GETTYAnother gold has followed for Team GB in the women's quad sculls.It means Team GB now has six to their name, which is quite the achievement.And Lola Anderson was delighted, with the 26-year-old saying: \\\"We spent ages working towards this and as a boat we are so process-driven, we are always looking to what comes next but when you are getting towards the end of a cycle like this, and it does not get bigger than this, it's quite overwhelming to experience this, but really grateful.\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 3317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2459, \"end\": 2469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6285494837002567e-35, \"text\": \"Mike Tyson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\"}, {\"begin\": 2538, \"end\": 2547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jake Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\"}, {\"begin\": 2611, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.523356957733917e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 2686, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.2358290699044558e-11, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2781, \"