\\"It's been a long time in the making and I still can not quite believe it.Team GB celebrate winning gold in the women's sculls|PA\\\"I do not know if I am emotional yet but that will come.\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3417, \"end\": 3419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9457771835931281, \"rank\": 0.05733137759458789, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we were so process-driven today and the immensity of what this is, it has not caught up with me.\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The crew today were amazing.\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We kept it so cool to the end.\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We had the confidence, we have done so many hard miles in training and for anyone out there just go for it.\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you think you can you might just do it one day, and that's the really cool thing about the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There had been doubts over whether the event would go ahead amid concerns over the pollution levels of the River Seine.\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 4022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4010, \"end\": 4021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers had previously said there was only a 60 per cent chance of the waters being fit for humans to compete in but, after a check at 03:20 on Wednesday, results from the latest water analyses deemed conditions compliant.\", \